      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "加氢裂化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "使用负载在MCM-22、MCM-36、MCM-41和MCM-48四种不同载体上的磷化铁(FeP)催化剂，在高压反应器中对棕榈油进行加氢裂化反应，生产生物航空燃料。反应条件为400°C、20 bar氢气压力、3小时反应时间，以环己烷为溶剂。",
        "text_snippet": "The reaction was performed in the high-pressure Parr reactor. Firstly,3.7mlofpalmoiland0.3gofcatalystwereloadedintoanautoclavewhile40mlofcyclohexanewasfilledassolvent.Airwaseliminatedfromasystembyhydrogenpurgesfor5minandahydrogengaswaspressedintoasystemfor20bars.Thereactionwasprocessedat400°Cfor3hwith300rpmofstirring.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
